reviewText: One of my favorite shows of all time!  It has a terrific cast, and is very well written.  I would highly recommend it!
Great show and the DVDs are in great condition!!!! My wife has been watching them while on vacation and had greatly enjoyed herself!!

We received some "bootleg" copies...not sure why...The reason I know this is because the DVDs do not work in blue ray player or any high end DVD player. They come up as a Data disk and will not play. The only type of player they will work on is a small cheaper brand of DVD player. So it limits where I can watch them.
Hard to stop watching. Love to watch a disc at a time. Acting and script are great, the video quality leaves a little to be desired.

I love this show but the quality of these dvds were horrible. Amost as if they had been bootlegged.  The last couple of episodes on all the disc started tiling and were very grainy.  I would not recommend anyone buy these disc.
The shows were great, but there was some freezes and a skip in the first season's discs. I would recommend it.

The first disc loaded into the machine and played fitfully... in places the picture devolved into a blur of pixels and faces were not visible... I was concerned because the disc was painted a mono-toned gray color instead of the color that it comes from the manufacturer... this gray color is famous at netflix for the re-burnt discs they are allowed to make by the people who sell them their licenses... with them it's legal, with this I was wondering.  Disc two and three would not play in my machine and that's when I gave up and sent them back.
I always wanted to see this serial.  It is really good.  The only one thing that I missed was the subtitles in Spanish.
Modern day life, love and everything in between!! Watch closely and it will tell you what really matters when it comes to love....highly entertaining, well written and seductively addictive!!!
For my money, one of the best series you can buy.
Great series with a depraved humor. Duchovny at his finest. Show got a bit weaker after season 4, but I still loved it.
The series was excellent. However the quality of the DVD transfer is atrocious. I wouldn't even buy the whole series for $1! It is just too painful to attempt to watch.
great price, best series Ive ever seen on TV, a must own for every guy

It took over a month to get the DVDs, but I think that was more of a Post Office problem. Our P.O. out here stinks- they constantly lose our mail. The quality was fine. The show is edgy and funny although I think the writers definitely ripped off Kevin Smith....BIG TIME!
Snarky and irreverent. Humorous and sexy. A wonderful commentary on a slice of contemporary life. Disturbing and delightful. Fabulously entertaining.
This is up there with Shameless.
